<p>Ecosystem restoration =</p>
<ol>
<li>&nbsp;of lands previously converted to agriculture</li>
<li>of degraded ecosystems</li></ol>
<p><strong>Approaches to biodiversity conservation :&nbsp;</strong></p>
<p>while a focus on protecting <u><em>intact</em></u> ecosystems can yield the greatest gains for terrestrial biodiversity, an emphasis on improving biodiversity in <u><em>‘shared’ landscapes</em></u> such as farmed land generates greater gains for services such as pest control, erosion control and pollination, as well as for aquatic biodiversity</p>